Welcome to this minimalist introduction to Python programming!
This course is designed for absolute beginners who have no prior experience with programming or Python. 
By the end of this course, you will have a basic understanding of Python syntax, data types, control structures, functions, and file operations.

Course Requirements
To take this course, you will need a computer with an internet connection and a web browser. 
You will also need to install Python on your computer. We will provide instructions on how to install Python in Module 1.

Conclusion
We hope this course provides you with a solid foundation in Python programming.
If you have any questions or feedback about this course, please don't hesitate to contact us. Good luck and happy coding!
